<H3><A NAME="passwd.History"></A>passwd.History</A></h3>
d747 3
a749 11
<P>
<I>Npasswd</i> can maintain
password history to discourage too-frequent reuse.
<P>
See the
<A HREF="PasswordChecks.html#check_history">history section</a>
of <A HREF="PasswordChecks.html">The Anatomy of Password Checking</a>
for details.
